short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Converts all open tabs into a list of links in a Markdown file.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension will convert all tabs open in the current window into a Markdown file.

Increase your productivity by saving your links to a text document without the need for saving individual bookmarks. 

- The generated markdown file will be directed to your Downloads folder.

- If a title is not provided the Markdown file will be titled: "tabsToMarkdown_MM-DD-YYYY .md".
